    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "38460307_5_543-578",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "543-578",
      "markText": "且夫孝始于事亲，中于事君，终于立身。扬名于后世，以显父母，此孝之大者。",
      "totalCount": 39,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=38460307&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=543&rangeEnd=578",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0ad32770724adb930adb45f?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=543&rangeEnd=578"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "38460307_7_1025-1044",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "1025-1044",
      "markText": "讥讽议论别人，而且爱结交轻薄任侠之士。",
      "totalCount": 39,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=38460307&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1025&rangeEnd=1044",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0ad32770724adb930adb45f?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1025&rangeEnd=1044"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "38460307_6_1227-1256",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "1227-1256",
      "markText": "如今你还这么年轻，就得到了黄门侍郎的官职，这是显要的职位。",
      "totalCount": 36,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=38460307&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1227&rangeEnd=1256",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0ad32770724adb930adb45f?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1227&rangeEnd=1256"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "38460307_6_484-505",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "484-505",
      "markText": "言有忧则恐惧敬事，敬事则必有善功而福至也。",
      "totalCount": 34,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=38460307&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=484&rangeEnd=505",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0ad32770724adb930adb45f?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=484&rangeEnd=505"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "38460307_11_410-464",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "410-464",
      "markText": "闻汝充役，室如悬磬①，何以自辨？论德则吾薄，说居则吾贫。勿以薄而志不壮，贫而行不高也。",
      "totalCount": 34,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=38460307&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=410&rangeEnd=464",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0ad32770724adb930adb45f?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=410&rangeEnd=464"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "38460307_7_1061-1131",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "1061-1131",
      "markText": "我希望你们听到别人的过失，如同听到了父母的名字，耳朵可以听，但嘴里不能说出来。喜欢议论别人的长短，轻率地讽刺讥评国家法度，这些都是我最厌恶的",
      "totalCount": 33,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=38460307&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1061&rangeEnd=1131",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0ad32770724adb930adb45f?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1061&rangeEnd=1131"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "38460307_6_896-926",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "896-926",
      "markText": "如果没有非常好的品德，而承受的恩惠却很丰厚，那将如何报答呢？",
      "totalCount": 32,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=38460307&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=896&rangeEnd=926",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0ad32770724adb930adb45f?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=896&rangeEnd=926"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "38460307_6_959-996",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "959-996",
      "markText": "有忧患便会恐惧而谨慎地做事，恐惧而谨慎地做事就必定有大功，从而使福运降临。",
      "totalCount": 32,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=38460307&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=959&rangeEnd=996",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0ad32770724adb930adb45f?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=959&rangeEnd=996"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "38460307_11_1134-1196",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "1134-1196",
      "markText": "品行修养的最高境界就是慎独，看似漫长实际短暂的一生将会历经不同的境遇，但无论富有还是贫穷，我们都应固守内心，坚持自己的原则。",
      "totalCount": 32,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=38460307&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=1134&rangeEnd=1196",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0ad32770724adb930adb45f?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=1134&rangeEnd=1196"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "38460307_40_3689-3698",
      "chapterUid": 40,
      "range": "3689-3698",
      "markText": "亲而宜恶，爱之为偏",
      "totalCount": 30,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=38460307&chapterUid=40&rangeStart=3689&rangeEnd=3698",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0ad32770724adb930adb45f?chapterUid=40&rangeStart=3689&rangeEnd=3698"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "38460307_42_1138-1186",
      "chapterUid": 42,
      "range": "1138-1186",
      "markText": "善须是积，今日积，明日积，积小便大。一念之差，一言之差，一事之差，有因而丧身亡家者，岂不可畏也？",
      "totalCount": 30,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=38460307&chapterUid=42&rangeStart=1138&rangeEnd=1186",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0ad32770724adb930adb45f?chapterUid=42&rangeStart=1138&rangeEnd=1186"
    },
    {
